description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 moving puzzles are included.
-Dozing American Shorthair Kitten
-Three Maine Coon kittens
-Scottish Fold looking around restlessly
-Two kittens napping together
-Two American Shorthair kittens
-Two Scottish Fold kittens
-Kitten Grooming
-Kitten playing with soccer ball
-Maine Coon kittens on fluffy bed
-Maine Coon kitten in a pet bed
name: [Moving] Fluffy Kittens
